    "Initially, a meticulous data preprocessing phase is conducted on the existing locomotive maintenance data to assemble a comprehensive and structured locomotive maintenance dataset.",
    "This refined dataset is subsequently utilized to generate LLMs customized specifically for locomotives.",
    "A data standardization tool is subsequently developed and ground in a customized locomotive LLM.",
    "Finally, a multiround dialog dataset is formulated, which serves as the foundation for designing an intelligent maintenance Q&A system anchored in a customized locomotive LLM.",
    "In summary, the contributions of this study are as follows:"
